data.description: Look no further, this beautiful home has a lot to offer! Very well-maintained property that looks and smell like new, completely fenced with nice size backyard and pavers through the entire floor with above the ground pool and spacious gazebo ideal for all your outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying the privacy in your own oasis. This is a move-in ready 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage, cozy home with great layout with a welcome entrance, ample kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and soft water system for the full house perfect for any family. Low HOA with no CDD. Fantastic location, around 20 minutes from Lake Nona area, shopping and dining options along Narcoossee Rd.
